DocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532832\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2532832\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 16, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104usv1665702767252.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/usv1665702767252.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/usv1665702767252.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"usv1665702767252\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      ioprint\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"usv1665702767252__ioprint_66363\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Select the I/O messages sent to the message frame.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"usv1665702767252__topic_d19394e1_d19395e1_d19396e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"usv1665702767252__p_d19397e1_d19398e1_d19399e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">IOprint</code> {<var class=\"keyword varname\">MessageLevel</var>}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"usv1665702767252__topic_d13962e1_d13963e1_d13964e1_d13965e1_d13966e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d914891e65\">\n                        \n Arguments\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"usv1665702767252__p_d19403e1_d19404e1_d19405e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">MessageLevel</var>—integer representing the sum of the message codes for the desired message types. If the sum of the codes is <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>, no information is placed in the message frame. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nqh1665702549702.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nqh1665702549702.html\" title=\"Most of the messages that display in the message frame are determined by the I/O message level. The I/O message is a number that is determined by adding up the codes of the applicable message types.\">I/O Message Levels</a>.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"usv1665702767252__topic_d13967e1_d13968e1_d13969e1_d13970e1_d13971e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d914891e87\">\n                        \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"usv1665702767252__p_d19409e1_d19410e1_d19411e1\">The value specified overrides the current definition for the message level defined with <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/pri</span>, or in the application shell.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"usv1665702767252__p_d19412e1_d19413e1_d19414e1\">If the sum of codes is 0, no information is placed in the message frame.</p>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The following command sends the following messages to the message frame:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"usv1665702767252__li_d9515e1_d9516e1_d9517e1\">Store sequence messages (code=1)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"usv1665702767252__li_d9518e1_d9519e1_d9520e1\">Connector function calls (code=2)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"usv1665702767252__li_d9521e1_d9522e1_d9523e1\">Fetch and Select return values (code=4)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"usv1665702767252__li_d9524e1_d9525e1_d9526e1\">Open description block (code = 8)\n </li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"usv1665702767252__section_nwl_llb_tcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d914891e123\">Example:</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"usv1665702767252__p_d19418e1_d19419e1_d19420e1\">The sum of the desired codes (1+2+4+8=15) is used for\n            the requested <var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var>.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"usv1665702767252__pre_nlt_llb_tcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">io 15</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532832\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532832\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "ioprint Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 16, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 ioprint Select the I/O messages sent to the message frame. IOprint { MessageLevel } Arguments MessageLevel —integer representing the sum of the message codes for the desired message types. If the sum of the codes is 0 , no information is placed in the message frame. For more information, see I/O Message Levels . Description The value specified overrides the current definition for the message level defined with /pri , or in the application shell. If the sum of codes is 0, no information is placed in the message frame. The following command sends the following messages to the message frame: Store sequence messages (code=1) Connector function calls (code=2) Fetch and Select return values (code=4) Open description block (code = 8) Example: The sum of the desired codes (1+2+4+8=15) is used for the requested Value . io 15 Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}